[![Markta.dev home page](/markata.dev_.webp)](https://markata.dev){.shadow-2xl}
Markata builds it's own docs in completely in `markata` using all built in templatates and plugins.
[![Markta.dev home page](/markata.dev_markata_plugins_base-cli_.webp)](https://https://markata.dev/markata/plugins/base-cli/){.shadow-2xl}
Using the `markata.plugins.docs` plugin it is able to load all the python files. It renders out all the docstrings as markdown and shows the code in highlighted code blocks.
